::'''Ctesiphona:''' Did I experience... a rebirth? Just moments ago, I was bound to the Dawn Device, facing my brother's judgment. His visage grew fierce as he uttered the command, instantly eradicating the Titan blood from within me...
::'''Ctesiphona:''' ...In my previous life, I was the prophesied savior of Amphoreus. My birth instilled hope in every faithful disciple of Cerces, with the Grove sparing no expense in bringing me up for the day when I am prophesied to stand against the encroaching black tide.
::'''Ctesiphona:''' Little did they suspect that I was the great-great-great-great... granddaughter of Thanatos' clandestine lineage, fated to sow death and disorder in the realm of mortals. Following Cerces' will, my brother imbibed the golden blood and executed me personally to prevent further calamity.
::'''Ctesiphona:''' In this new life, I vow to reclaim what is rightfully mine...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Wait a sec. This is getting too whimsical!
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} The time I was reincarnated as the librarium owner.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Let's just skip the ads.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504003017-->
::'''Ctesiphona:''' Hmm... I guess... I must've been dreaming about the new story I wrote last night, hehehe.
::'''Ctesiphona:''' I've gotten used to the routine of running the store and sleeping by day, and writing at night, but coming up with a plot on the spot is a first for me. Maybe my tale is just too engrossing this time!
::'''Ctesiphona:''' Hey, you! Forget what I just said and don't mention it to anyone. If my brother finds out... I'm toast.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} But it's nice to have dreams, right?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504003021-->
:::'''Ctesiphona:''' Well... simply put... he thinks that we as followers of Cerces should not...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Would he "instantly eradicate" you?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504003023-->
:::'''Ctesiphona:''' Well, something like that. Simply put... he thinks that we as followers of Cerces should not...
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504003024-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504003024-->
::'''Ctesiphona:''' Shh... we've got a customer. Let's catch up later.
